### Pre-mortem

| Risk | Type | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------|-----------|--------|------------|
| handlers unwrap() panics on DB errors | Paper Tiger | Low | Medium | DB inserts rarely fail; fix with proper error propagation in follow-up |
| Worker/API behavior divergence (separate handler code) | Elephant | Medium | Medium | Same SQL in both repos; shared domain types enforce contract; integration test on live URL |
| Single D1 database = single point of failure | Tiger | Low | High | D1 has automatic backups; future: multi-region federation |
| No auth on admin endpoints | Tiger | High | Medium | MVP scope — add Supabase Auth before public launch |

- Unmitigated Tigers: 0 (auth is known MVP debt, not this track's scope)
