3. [MINOR] Unused import in `crates/api/src/sqlite_repo.rs:705` — `CreateCourierRequest`

### Recommendations
- Replace `unwrap()` in handlers with proper error propagation (match on RepoError → HTTP status)
- Remove unused import in sqlite_repo.rs
- Add README.md with setup/run/deploy instructions
